ry Bolotov]]<br />{{small|(<small>May-Aug</small> 2014)}}\n| commander2  = [[File:Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Volodymyr Zelensky]]'''<br />{{small|(since 2019)}}<br>[[File:Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Petro Poroshenko]]'''<br />{{small|(2014\u20132019)}}<br>{{nowrap|[[File:Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Oleksandr Turchynov]]'''}}<br />{{small|(<small>Feb\u2013Jun</small> 2014)}}<br>{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Stepan Poltorak]]<br />{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Mykhailo Kutsyn]]<br />{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Serhiy Hayduk]]\n| units1      = {{flagicon image|Flag of the Russian Federation Ground Forces.svg}} [[Russian Ground Forces|'''Ground Forces''']]:\n* [[18th Guards Motor Rifle Brigade]]<ref name=\"\u0412 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043d\u043a\u043e\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0445\u043e\u0434\u044f\u0442\u0441\u044f \u0432\u043e\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430 \u0427\u0435\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0420\u0435\u0441\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0438\"/>\n* 9th Motorized Rifle Brigade ([[Nizhny Novgorod]])<ref name=\"tg01xaa\">{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/sep/03/ukraine-soldier-youre-better-clueless-because-truth-horrible-moscow-ilovaysk|title=Russian soldier: 'You're better clueless because the truth is horrible'|author=Shaun Walker|author2=Oksana Grytsenko|author3=Leonid Ragozin|work=[[The Guardian]]|date=4 September 2014|accessdate=21 March 2015}}</ref>\n* [[200th Independent Motor Rifle Brigade|200th Motor Rifle Brigade]]<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.bellingcat.com/news/uk-and-europe/2016/06/21/russias-200th-motorized-infantry-brigade-in-the-donbass-part-2/ | title=Russia's 200th Motorized Infantry Brigade in the Donbass: The Hero of Russia | accessdate=21 June 2016 | date=21 June 2016}}</ref>\n{{flagicon image|Flag of the Russian Airborne Troops.svg}} [[Russian Airborne Troops|'''Airborne Troops''']]:<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pln-pskov.ru/society/162318.html|scr