ailybeast.com/articles/2014/03/01/so-russia-invaded-crimea.html|title=Russia Stages a Coup in Crimea|newspaper=The Daily Beast|date=3 January 2014|author=Michael Weiss|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2014/03/04/world/europe/ukraine-mood-on-the-ground/index.html?hpt=bosread|title=An eerie mood on the ground in Crimea |publisher=CNN |accessdate=30 December 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=Lizzie Dearden|title=Ukraine crisis: Putin asks Russian parliament's permission for military invasion in Crimea|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/ukraine-crisis-putin-asks-russian-parliaments-permission-for-military-invasion-in-crimea-9162253.html|newspaper=The Independent|date=1 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015|location=London}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://interfax.com.ua/news/general/194157.html|script-title=ru:\u0420\u043e\u0441\u0441\u0438\u044f \u043d\u0435\u0437\u0430\u043a\u043e\u043d\u043d\u043e \u0443\u0432\u0435\u043b\u0438\u0447\u0438\u043b\u0430 \u0447\u0438\u0441\u043b\u0435\u043d\u043d\u043e\u0441\u0442\u044c \u0441\u0432\u043e\u0438\u0445 \u0432\u043e\u0439\u0441\u043a \u0432 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0438\u043d\u0435 \u0434\u043e 16 \u0442\u044b\u0441. \u2013 \u0438.\u043e. \u043c\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0430 \u043e\u0431\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u044b|language=ru|trans-title=Russia illegally increased the number of its troops in Ukraine up to 21 thousand - Acting Minister of Defence|agency=Interfax.ua|date=3 March 2014|accessdate=11 January 2015}}</ref>\u201342,000<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/insider-view-moscow-control-ukraine-crimea-article-1.1708580|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306053739/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/insider-view-moscow-control-ukraine-crimea-article-1.1708580|archivedate=6 March 2014 |title=Insider's view: Moscow is in control of Crimea in Ukraine|date=3 March 2014|work=Daily News|location=New York|accessda