an Tatar People]] \n----\n{{small|'''Supported by:'''}}<br />{{flag|NATO}}<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-29198497|title=Nato members 'send arms to Ukraine'|date=14 September 2014|via=www.bbc.com|work=BBC News}}</ref><br />{{small|(arms, [[military exercises]], and general [[aid]])}}\n| commander1  = [[File:Standard of the President of the Russian Federation.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Vladimir Putin]]'''<br />{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Sergey Shoygu]]<br />{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Valery Gerasimov]]<br />{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Igor Korobov]]<br />{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Aleksandr Vitko]]<br />{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Denis Berezovsky]]<br />{{nowrap|{{flagicon|Russia}} [[Alexander Lentsov]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k7_3t56yDvw|title=Russian Lieutenant General Alexander Lentsov leading Russian groups in Debaltseve|publisher=YouTube, LifeNews|date=18 February 2015|accessdate=18 February 2015}}</ref>}}<br />{{small|'''In Crimea:'''}}<br />{{flagicon|Republic of Crimea}} [[Sergey Aksyonov]]<br />{{small|'''In Donbass:'''}}<br />{{flagicon|Donetsk People's Republic}} [[Denis Pushilin]]<br />{{small|(since 2018)}}<br>{{flagicon|Donetsk People's Republic}} [[Dmitry Trapeznikov]]<br />{{small|({{small|Aug-Sep}} 2018)}}<br />{{nowrap|{{flagicon|Donetsk People's Republic}} [[Alexander Zakharchenko|A. Zakharchenko]]{{KIA}}}}<br />{{small|(2014\u20132018)}}<br />{{flagicon|Lugansk People's Republic}} [[Leonid Pasechnik]]<br />{{small|(since 2017)}}<br />{{flagicon|Lugansk People's Republic}} [[Igor Plotnitsky]]<br />{{small|(2014\u20132017)}}<br />{{flagicon|Lugansk People's Republic}} [[Valery Bolotov]]<br />{{small|(<small>May-Aug</small> 2014)}}\n| commander2  = [[File:Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Volodymyr Zelensky]]'''<br />{{small|(since 2019)}}<br>[[File:Flag of the President of Ukraine.svg|22px|border]] '''[[Petro Poroshenko]]'''<br />{{small|(2014\u20132019)}}<br>{{nowrap|[[File:Flag of the President of Ukra