orne Division|98th Airborne Division]]\n* [[31st Guards Airborne Brigade|31st Airborne Brigade]]\n{{flagicon image|Naval Ensign of Russia.svg}} [[Russian Navy|'''Navy''']]:\n* [[Baltic Fleet]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ukrinform.ua/eng/news/russia_redeploys_ships_of_baltic_and_northern_fleets_to_sevastopol_violates_agreement_with_ukraine_317983|title=Russia redeploys ships of Baltic and Northern fleets to Sevastopol, violates agreement with Ukraine|agency=Ukrinform|date=3 March 2014|accessdate=30 December 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910085436/http://www.ukrinform.ua/eng/news/russia_redeploys_ships_of_baltic_and_northern_fleets_to_sevastopol_violates_agreement_with_ukraine_317983|archive-date=10 September 2015|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* [[Northern Fleet]]\n* [[Black Sea Fleet]]\n** [[File:Morskaja pehota Rossii.gif|20px]] [[Naval Infantry (Russia)|Marines]]\n[[File:Emblem of the GRU.svg|22px]] [[Main Intelligence Directorate (Russia)|'''GRU''']]:<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/01/us-ukraine-crisis-military-idUSKCN0JF1ZN20141201|title=Ukraine says Russian special forces involved in attacks on airport in east|work=Reuters|accessdate= 11 April 2015|date=1 December 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"\u0412 \u0414\u0436\u0430\u043d\u043a\u043e\u0435 \u043d\u0430\u0445\u043e\u0434\u044f\u0442\u0441\u044f \u0432\u043e\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430 \u0427\u0435\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0441\u043a\u043e\u0439 \u0420\u0435\u0441\u043f\u0443\u0431\u043b\u0438\u043a\u0438\"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://maailm.postimees.ee/2718018/ukraina-krimmis-on-tsetseeniast-ja-uljanovskist-parit-vene-sodurid|title=Ukraina: Krimmis on T\u0161et\u0161eeniast ja Uljanovskist p\u00e4rit Vene s\u00f5durid|trans-title=Ukraine:In Crimea there are Russian troops from Chechnya and Ulyanovsk|publisher=Postimees|language=et|date=5 March 2014|accessdate=16 September 2014}}</ref><ref name=\"Interest\">{{cite news|last1=Interest|first1=The National|title=Get Ready, America: Russia Has Its Own Deadly 'Delta Force'|url=http://nationalinterest.org/blog/the-buzz/get-ready-america-russia-has-its-own-deadly-delta-force-19793|accessdate=12 April 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"Crimea, 2014\">{{cite book|last1=Galeotti|first1=Mark|title=Spetsnaz: Russia's Special Forces|date=2015|publisher=Osprey Publishing|location=Oxford, UK|isbn=978-1-4728-0722-9|pages=50|edition=Elite|url=https://ospreypublishing.com/spetsnaz-russia-s-special-forces|accessdate=11 April 2017}}</ref>\n* [[Main Intelligence Directorate (Russia)#Activities|22nd Spetsnaz Brigade]]\n* [[45th Detached Reconnaissance Regiment|45th Guards Spetsnaz Regiment]]\n| units2      = {{Flagicon image|Ensign of the Ukrainian Ground Forces.svg}} [[Ukrainian Ground Forces|'''Ground Forces''']]:\n* [[Territorial defence battalion (Ukraine)|Territorial defence battalions]]\n{{flagicon image|Flag of Airmobile troops of Ukraine.svg}} [[Ukrainian Air Assault Forces|'''Air Assault Forces''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Ensign of the Ukrainian Air Force.svg}} [[Ukrainian Air Force|'''Air Force''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Naval Ensign of Ukraine.svg}} [[Ukrainian Navy|'''Navy''']]<br />{{flagicon image|Flag_of_the_National_Guard_of_Ukraine.svg}} [[National Guard of Ukraine|'''National Guard''']]:\n* [[Right Sector]]\n* [[Azov Battalion]]\n* [[Donbas Battalion]]\n[[File:\u0413\u0435\u0440\u0430\u043b\u044c\u0434\u0438\u0447\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0437\u043d\u0430\u043a - \u0435\u043c\u0431\u043b\u0435\u043c\u0430 \u041c\u0412\u0421 \u0423\u043a\u0440\u0430\u0457\u043d\u0438.svg|20px]] [[Special Tasks Patrol Police (Ukraine)|'''Special tasks patrol police''']]:\n* [[Dnipro Battalion]]\n* [[Kharkiv Police Battalion|Kharkiv Battalion]]\n[[File:Emblem of the State Border Guard Service of Ukraine.svg|20px]] [[State Border Guard Service of Ukraine|'''State Border Guard''']]:\n* [[Noman \u00c7elebicihan Battalion]]\n[[File:Security Service of Ukraine Emblem.svg|20px]] [[Security Service of Ukraine|'''Security Service''']]:\